text: The eleventh season of SpongeBob SquarePants started on July 27, 2017. It started with the episodes "Spot Returns" and "The Check-Up". It ended on November 25, 2018 with the episode "Goons on the Moon." Stephen Hillenburg, the show's creator, was the executive producer. Marc Ceccarelli and Vincent Waller were the showrunners. ==Episodes== == DVD release == The DVD boxset for season eleven was released by Paramount Home Entertainment and Nickelodeon in the United States and Canada on March 31, 2020. The DVD release features bonus materials, including the animated short "Plankton's Color Nullifier".
